schools.name: Ann Brock El At Oak Grove

data.description: Sellers are offering a $5k concession to buyers that buyers may use towards closing costs or rate buy down. Sought after 4 bed 2 bath home close to shopping, dining, I-635W, I-20, HWY 287, & HWY 67. Six Flags, AT&T Stadium, and so much more. Conveniently located in Burleson ISD and around the block from the community pool! Take a break on your spacious front porch as temperatures cool this fall season, and head inside to the exceptional open floor plan with soaring ceilings in this unique home in desirable Ashford Park. Save on your monthly expenses with no city taxes! Spend more time where it matters on your extra large private back patio, and less time cleaning in this carpet free home. The owners suite offers extra space for a sitting area, and a remodeled decorative tile surround shower with a luxury stye rain shower head! Soak in the garden tup as you relax the days stress away. Lots of storage throughout as one of the secondary bedrooms has a huge walk-in closet.
